#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn23.34"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.34:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.34:0.2"
msgid "3. Āyācanavagga "
msgstr "3. Appeals "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Nirodhadhammasutta "
msgstr "34. Liable To Cease "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn23.34:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.34:1.2"
msgid "Āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.34:1.3"
msgid "“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto vihareyyan”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo. "
msgstr "“Rādha, you should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever is liable to cease. "

msgctxt "sn23.34:2.2"
msgid "Ko ca, rādha, nirodhadhammo? "
msgstr "And what is liable to cease? "

msgctxt "sn23.34:2.3"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Form is liable to cease. You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.4"
msgid "vedanā nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.5"
msgid "saññā nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.6"
msgid "saṅkhārā nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.7"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe … "
msgstr "Consciousness is liable to cease. You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for it. "

#. VAR: ti → bj potthake pana imasmiṃ vagge chattiṃsa suttāni vibhattāni ekekaṃ suttaṃ tīṇi tīṇi katvā, evaṃ
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.8"
msgid "yo kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo”ti. "
msgstr "You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever is liable to cease.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.9"
msgid "Āyācanavaggo tatiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.200, sc3
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.1"
msgid "Māro ca māradhammo ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.2"
msgid "Aniccena apare duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.3"
msgid "Dukkhena ca duve vuttā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.4"
msgid "Anattena tatheva ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.5"
msgid "Khayavayasamudayaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.6"
msgid "Nirodhadhammena dvādasāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
